{
  "texts": [
    "These are, on his view, composed of strings of basic actions and their consequences.",
    "In his paper 'Agency ' (2001a, pp. 43-61), he gives a straightforward example: tying one's shoelaces.",
    "Of this kind of case, he writes:",
    "Synthese (2025) 205:47",
    "When I tie my shoelaces, there is on one hand the movement of my fingers, and on the other hand the movement of the laces."
  ]
}